    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The engine and transmission are strong, offering a smooth and reliable driving experience suitable for daily commutes or longer trips. While it shows some minor signs of previous use, the interior is clean and all major systems are functioning as they should. You can expect a dependable car that is ready for the road with no immediate major repairs required.",
      "price": 35000.0,
